<main>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <video autoplay muted playsinline class="background-video">
        <source src="https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/508db523b4934728aeb0262266bb9d60.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        Your browser does not support the video tag.
      </video>
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="timer-box">Limited Time Offer - Ending Soon!</div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">
          Win Your
          <span>Dream Car</span>
          Today!
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          Purchase any item from our store and automatically get entered to
 
            win this incredible vehicle. Plus, receive BONUS entries with
            every $50 spent!
        </p>

        <!-- <div class="countdown">
          <div class="countdown-item">
            <span class="countdown-number" id="days">29</span>
            <span class="countdown-label">Days</span>
          </div>
          <div class="countdown-item">
            <span class="countdown-number" id="hours">23</span>
            <span class="countdown-label">Hours</span>
          </div>
          <div class="countdown-item">
            <span class="countdown-number" id="minutes">59</span>
            <span class="countdown-label">Minutes</span>
          </div>
          <div class="countdown-item">
            <span class="countdown-number" id="seconds">59</span>
            <span class="countdown-label">Seconds</span>
          </div>
        </div> -->

        <a href="#entry" class="cta-button">ENTER NOW</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Why Participate?</h2>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          {% comment %} <img
            src="#"
            alt="Easy Entry"
            class="feature-img" /> {% endcomment %}
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3 class="feature-title">Easy Entry</h3>
            <p class="feature-desc">
              Simply make any purchase on our store and you're automatically
 
                entered to win. Plus, get bonus entries with every $50 spent!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          {% comment %} <img
            src="#"
            alt="Guaranteed Winner"
            class="feature-img" /> {% endcomment %}
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3 class="feature-title">Guaranteed Winner</h3>
            <p class="feature-desc">
              Unlike other giveaways, we GUARANTEE a winner will be selected.
 
                Someone WILL drive away in this dream car!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          {% comment %} <img
            src="#"
            alt="Transparent Process"
            class="feature-img" /> {% endcomment %}
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3 class="feature-title">Transparent Process</h3>
            <p class="feature-desc">
              Our winner selection is conducted live and publicly. Fair and
 
                transparent with a trusted third-party verification.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="prize-showcase" id="prize">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Your Dream Car Awaits</h2>
      <div class="prize-content">
        <img
          src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0667/8036/4971/files/photo_2025-04-22_14-49-29.jpg?v=1745318990"
          alt="Luxury Car Prize"
          class="car-image" />
        <div class="car-details">
          <p>
            This stunning Chevrolet Corvette C8 HellBoar Edition comes fully loaded with premium
 
              leather interior, state-of-the-art entertainment system, advanced
              driver assistance features, and performance that will take your
              breath away. Valued at over
            <span class="highlight">$85,000</span>, this could be yours just
 
              by shopping with us!
          </p>
          <a href="#entry" class="cta-button">Win This Car</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="how-it-works" id="how-it-works">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Participation Process</h2>
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <h3 class="step-title">Choose your product</h3>
          <p>
            Browse our collection and make any purchase. Every order qualifies
 
              you for entry!
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <h3 class="step-title">Complete your purchase</h3>
          <p>
            Get 1 entry for any purchase, plus 1 BONUS entry for every $50
 
              spent on eligible products.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <h3 class="step-title">Receive your entry & wait for the draw</h3>
          <p>
            When the countdown ends, we'll randomly select and announce a
 
              winner who takes home the car!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="testimonials" id="testimonials">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Previous Winners</h2>
      <div class="testimonial-slider">
        <div class="testimonial-slide active">
          <p class="testimonial-text">
            "I never thought I'd actually win! When I got the call that I won
 
              last year's sports car, I couldn't believe it. The process was so
              smooth and the team was incredible throughout. Now I'm driving my
              dream car every day!"
          </p>
          <p class="testimonial-author">- Michael T., Last Year's Winner</p>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-slide">
          <p class="testimonial-text">
            "I only made a small purchase to support the brand, and next thing
 
              I know I'm picking up the keys to a brand new luxury vehicle! This
              giveaway changed my life completely. Forever grateful!"
          </p>
          <p class="testimonial-author">- Sarah J., Previous Winner</p>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-slide">
          <p class="testimonial-text">
            "The moment they announced my name during the live drawing was
 
              surreal. I've entered many giveaways before but this was the first
              legitimate one where they actually delivered exactly as promised.
              Truly amazing experience!"
          </p>
          <p class="testimonial-author">- Robert K., Grand Prize Winner</p>
        </div>

        <div class="slider-dots">
          <span class="dot active" data-slide="0"></span>
          <span class="dot" data-slide="1"></span>
          <span class="dot" data-slide="2"></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="faq" id="faq">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">How do I enter the giveaway?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
              To enter the giveaway, simply make any purchase on our website.
 
                Every order automatically qualifies you for entry, and you'll
                receive additional entries for every $50 spent on eligible
                products.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">When will the winner be announced?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
              The winner will be selected and announced when the countdown
 
                timer reaches zero. We conduct our drawing live on our social
                media channels to ensure complete transparency.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">What are the odds of winning?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
              Your odds of winning depend on the total number of entries
 
                received during the promotional period. The more you shop, the
                more entries you'll earn, which increases your chances of
                winning!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">Do I have to pay taxes if I win?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
              Winners are responsible for all taxes and fees associated with
 
                prize acceptance and use. We recommend consulting with a tax
                professional regarding your specific situation if you win.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">Can I win if I'm outside the US?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
              Yes! Our giveaway is open internationally. However,
 
                international winners may be responsible for additional
                shipping, import duties, taxes, and compliance with local
                regulations. We'll work with international winners to ensure a
                smooth delivery process.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">What if I don't want the car?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
              Winners have the option to choose a cash alternative of 75% of
 
                the vehicle's retail value. This gives you flexibility if you'd
                prefer the monetary prize instead of the vehicle itself.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

